com.stephengware.java.ai.planning.logic

Interface Literal

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Formula>, Expression, Formula
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NegatedLiteral, Predication

    public interface Literal
extends Expression
    A literal is an atomic expression (i.e. one which cannot be decomposed into smaller expressions) or the negation of such an atomic expression.
    Author:
    Stephen G. Ware
